<emphasis bold="true" box="[245,261,2015,2039]" pageId="58" pageNumber="59">I.</emphasis>
Two slides of holotype; 
<emphasis bold="true" box="[511,530,2015,2039]" pageId="58" pageNumber="59">J.</emphasis>
Labels.
